            <h2 class="font-serif text-[24px] text-parchment mb-[16px]">4. Authenticity Guarantee</h2>
            <p>Every timepiece listed on Wonder Watch has passed our multi-stage authentication protocol. In the rare event a piece is determined to be inauthentic post-delivery, we will arrange a full refund and collection at our expense. This guarantee is void if the piece has been tampered with, serviced, or modified without our prior written consent.</p>
