            <p>These terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of Maharashtra, India. Any disputes arising out of or in connection with these terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Mumbai, Maharashtra.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gold-faint pt-[32px]">
