            <p>For any legal enquiries, please contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@wonderwatch.in" class="text-gold hover:text-parchment transition-colors">legal@wonderwatch.in</a> or through our <a href="/contact" class="text-gold hover:text-parchment transition-colors">Concierge page</a>.</p>
